            "reviewBody": "I have been drinking Smith And Kearns for as long as I can remember! Delicious drink! We rarely have seltzer in the house, so I use a splash of cola instead, and half and half instead of cream. When I go to a bar, the bartenders almost never know what I'm talking about so I have to give them the ingredients."
